<![CDATA[<font style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Hi {!Account.Name},</font><div style="font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I wanted to pass along some more info about the "FastTrack</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">" feature so you're prepared to use it. &nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Here's how it works.</font></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2"><br></font></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-family: arial;">"FastTrack"&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">automatically detects new patients on the calendar and texts them a link to a unique, user-friendly digital form on their mobile device. After their new patient info is collected, a completed form is generated in the Lighthouse portal and can be downloaded as a PDF or printed out before the patient comes into the office.</font></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="">Previously, this feature was restricted to sending New Patient paperwork before a patient's first visit to your office. Now, we have added many questions to the form to use it as a post-COVID 19 screening questionnaire, as well as the ability to send the Patient Fast Track forms before <i>every</i> appointment! If you would like to do so, please let us know and we will update your account settings.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style=""><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">For more detailed information on "FastTrack</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">", please&nbsp; see the attached document. If you have a